title: A Cat Massage Parlor
description:
The massage salon that Nekoyama-kun, an exhausted office worker, had visited was a healing paradise, where a cat masseuse performs the service! The one that engulfs his tired body... his eyes, his shoulder, his lower back is the shopkeeper's fluffy and round paws!!!! Moreover, Nekoyama-kun was on the verge of ascension to heaven when the young massage apprentices appeared...!

Enjoy the best relaxation given by these extremely adorable cats ♪
